<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675573>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Aegidinus guianensis, holotype, female (a, b, d), female, paratype of Ae. oreibates (c), female from Villa Napoleão, Brazil (e), male, holotype of Ae. oreibates (f), male, paratype of Ae. oreibates (g–i). Habitus in dorsal view (a, c, f), labels (b), female external genitalia (d, e), aedeagus in lateral (h) and ventral view (g), parameres in dorsal view (i)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675573/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675583>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Aegidinus cornutus, male (a, c, d, e), female (b, f). Habitus in dorsal view (a, b); female external genitalia (f); aedeagus in lateral (c) and ventral view (e); parameres in dorsal view (d)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675583/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675575>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Aegidinus steinheili, lectotype, male (a, d–f), male with erroneous label ‘Bresil Steinheil...’. (b), female, paralectotype (c, g). Habitus in dorsal view (a–c), female external genitalia (g), aedeagus in lateral (f) and ventral view (d), parameres in dorsal view (e)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675579>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Aegidinus spp. Ae. noriegai sp. nov., holotype (a–d), Ae. simulatus, male (e–h). Habitus in dorsal view (a, e); aedeagus in lateral (b, f) and ventral view (d, h); parameres in dorsal view (c, g)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675579/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675577>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Aegidinus spp. Aegidinus candezei, lectotype, male (a, e), male (b–d), female (h, k), female, holotype of Ae. sunidigea (g, j); Aegidinus sp., paralectotype of Ae. candezei (f, i, l). Habitus in dorsal view (a, g, h, i); labels (e, f); female external genitalia (j–l); aedeagus in lateral (b) and ventral view (c); parameres in dorsal view (d)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675577/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3675581>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Aegidinus colbyae, holotype male (a, e, d, f), paratype female (b, c). Habitus in dorsal view (a, b); female external genitalia (c); aedeagus in lateral (f) and ventral view (d); parameres in dorsal view (e)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3675581/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

